{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Explore inside the human body  as a COVID-virus. A single player, action-adventure, indie game created by a doctor.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Gameplay</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Single player</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Third person</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Punching</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Kicking</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Shooting magic projectiles</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Item attacks</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Climbing</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3423860/extras/Gif_Climbing_616x180.gif?t=1737090796\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Style</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Action-Adventure</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Souls-like elements</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Medieval mixed with biology style</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Platforming</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Character</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Play as a customized COVID-virus, choosing your own colors and surface protein shape.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3423860/extras/Gif_C1_616x180.gif?t=1737090796\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Goals</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Work your way through the body and infect as many cells as possible</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Collect resources to craft items</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Kill immune cells and immune proteins</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3423860/extras/Gif_InfectingCell_616x180.gif?t=1737090796\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Enemies</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">White blood cell warriors (Neutrophils)</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Spawner drone (B-cells)</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Shooter drone (Plasma cells)</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Wild spiders (C1 immune proteins)</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Wild worms (Protease protein)</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3423860/extras/Gif_PlasmaCell_616x180.gif?t=1737090796\" /> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Shooter drone (Plasma cell)</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3423860/extras/Gif_Neutrophil_616x180.gif?t=1737090796\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">White blood cell warriors (Neutrophils)</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Items and crafting</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Consumable biology-related items can be crafted from peptide resources collected through the maps by breaking bush-like proteins.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Maps</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Explore several maps in different parts of the human body.</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Airways</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Lung sac</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Nose</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Lymph Node</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3423860/extras/LevelLungs_2.44.1.png?t=1737090796\" /></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Lung airway</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3423860/extras/LevelLungSack_2.20.1.png?t=1737090796\" /></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Lung sac</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3423860/extras/LevelNose_2.17.1.png?t=1737090796\" /></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Nose with olfactory neurons (smell-sensing)</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3423860/extras/LevelLymphNode_2.21.1.png?t=1737090796\" /></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Lymph node with lymph vessels</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p></li></ul>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3423860/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1737090796","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3423860/page_bg_generated.jpg?t=1737090796","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3423860/4d679a8ed435ba1073c20850870508b76b5bec78/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1737090796","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3423860/4d679a8ed435ba1073c20850870508b76b5bec78/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1737090796","categories":[{"description":"Single-player","id":2},{"description":"